Description:
    Creates a hello_st2 stackstorm pack.

Options:
    Sensors: Include Sensors
    Rules: Create Rules
    Policies: Create Policies
    Aliases: Create Aliases

Example:
    yo st2pack

    This will create:
        actions: hello action.
        aliases: hello action alias
        policies: hello action policies
        rules: hello action rules
        sensors: hello action sensors

        app/: Your application files.
        test/: Unit tests for your application.